data.description: Welcome to the Silver Creek subdivision, where this two-story gem awaits your personal touch. Spanning 1582 sqft, this home features 3 cozy bedrooms and 2 baths, all set within a layout ready for your creative vision. The heart of the home boasts a welcoming fireplace in the living area, setting the stage for memorable gatherings. With no carpet throughout, the maintenance is a breeze, allowing more time to enjoy the space. Each bedroom offers ample room for rest and rejuvenation, while the large backyard with a covered patio promises endless outdoor enjoyment. Located in Northwest San Antonio, this well-maintained property is a canvas ready for your imagination to unfold.   NISD schools and public bus stop, public library & HEB, and Walmart nearby.
